# ============================================
# Vercel Auto-Populated (DO NOT SET MANUALLY)
# ============================================
# VERCEL=1
# VERCEL_ENV=production
# VERCEL_URL=auto-populated-by-vercel
# VERCEL_GIT_COMMIT_SHA=auto-populated-by-vercel
# VERCEL_GIT_COMMIT_REF=auto-populated-by-vercel

# ============================================
# IMPORTANT NOTES
# ============================================
# 1. Generate a strong JWT_SECRET (min 32 characters)
#    Example: openssl rand -base64 32
#
# 2. Update NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL with your actual Vercel domain
#    Example: https://nodesio.vercel.app
#
# 3. For production, consider changing default passwords:
#    - Generate new password hashes using SHA-256
#    - Update ADMIN_PASSWORD_HASH and DEMO_PASSWORD_HASH
#
# 4. All NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables are exposed to the browser
#    - Never put secrets in NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables
#
# 5. To add these to Vercel:
#    - Go to your project settings
#    - Navigate to "Environment Variables"
#    - Add each variable one by one
#    - Select "Production" environment
